I didn't know that before yesterday but it was a bad idea in fact :
openssl base64 doesn't handle utf8 encoded content. So i found recode
command.=20

finaly :

alias b64dec=3D'recode b64..data'
alias b64enc=3D'recode data..b64'

benches are welcome ;)

